Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 星白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之先回繼衛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實 Heigus粒子已經用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.54,0:06:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部都聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 就是不想變成這樣才沒有應答的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連你也 谷風沒有必要一起死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易把奇居子打倒了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heigus粒子收集膜打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去試試能不能手動打開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一 希德尼亞停下時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要能追上才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可真是肚子餓了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊嘞 星白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮 星白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.94,0:07:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生命維持物質有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空氣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:07:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經積存起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水夠兩個人生活2週啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍糧還有8個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 為了非常時期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保存了2個月的份量的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們能進行光合成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是綜合計算而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考慮到水和糧食
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道能不能熬過10天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就先睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要溫存體力才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谷風 今天辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.77,0:09:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水…水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟了 喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谷風 醒了嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我在進行光合成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不看 你可以繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才剛開始 幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:09:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谷風
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緊急時候的應對是在哪學的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 爺爺敎給我不少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在地下一起生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該還沒有接受多少訓練的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能十分明確的行動 讓我吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.94,0:10:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說過無論在哪裏 為了活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都要盡最大努力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一位好爺爺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
