Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？ 谷風
